---
layout: base.njk
title: The Journal
description: "Honest, helpful guidance for couples planning a wedding in Oregon & SW Washington — from timelines and budgets to weather, vendors, and peace of mind."
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <p class="section__eyebrow">For the Bride-to-Be</p>
  <h1 class="page-hero__title">The Journal</h1>
  <p class="page-hero__sub">Real answers to the questions I hear most — written to make your planning calmer, clearer, and a little more joyful.</p>
</section>

<section class="bloglist">
  {% if collections.blog.length %}
  <div class="bloglist__grid">
    {% for post in collections.blog %}
    <a class="postcard" href="{{ post.url }}">
      {% if post.data.cover %}<div class="postcard__img"><img src="{{ post.data.cover }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }}" loading="lazy" /></div>{% endif %}
      <div class="postcard__body">
        <p class="postcard__date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</p>
        <h2 class="postcard__title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
        <p class="postcard__excerpt">{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <span class="postcard__more">Read More →</span>
      </div>
    </a>
    {% endfor %}
  </div>
  {% else %}
  <p class="bloglist__empty">New stories are on the way — check back soon.</p>
  {% endif %}
</section>

<section class="cta-band">
  <div class="cta-band__inner">
    <p class="section__eyebrow">Have a Question I Haven't Answered?</p>
    <h2 class="section__title">Just ask — I'm happy to help.</h2>
    <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--dark">Get in Touch</a>
  </div>
</section>
